name: 娜塔莎·瓦斯鲁克
name_full: 娜塔莎·瓦斯鲁克 Natasha Vasiluk
introduction: Natalia Vasiluk was born on January 23, 1963 in Kharkiv, Ukraine. Graduated in 1985 from the Ukrainian Academy of Arts, Faculty of Movie, Drama and Musical Theatre. Natalia performed more than 50 Lead roles in theatres of Ukraine, Russia, Israel and Canada on Ukrainian, Russian, Hebrew, English and French languages.From 1993 Natalia resides in Vancouver, BC. Today, we know her for "Arrow" (2017), "Stargate" (2004), "The Chris Isaak Show" (2003), "The Outer Limits" (1999), "X-Files" (1997) and others.Natalia loves to work on set as a Russian/Ukrainian Dialect Coach and Choreographer as well.
